data.description: This immaculate home is located on a corner lot with a spacious open floor plan. The efficiently laid out kitchen is a chef's dream with beautiful, custom mahogany stained cabinets. The primary bedroom boasts a custom walk-in closet and a spacious master bath with duel sinks, jetted tub, separate shower, and a medicine cabinet. The three other bedrooms are split from the primary.  Every window has 2 inch vinyl blinds. The airy entrance opens into a sitting room with the formal dining room steps away. As you walk through the home the great room opens up to the beautiful wood burning fireplace. The roof is only 5 years old, the HVAC system new in 2021, with a Garage door opener new in 2017.  Leased Solar panels make for a very low electric bill. The home is fully landscaped and features Red Tip Photinias for privacy and Morning Glories. Paving stones were laid with care for ease of traversing.  The Concrete patio is great for outdoor entertaining. Near to schools and shopping!
